import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"
import styles from "../styles/Navbar.css"
import {Button} from "@material-ui/core";

const Navbar = () => {

    return(
        <nav>
            <Button className={styles.link}>
                <NavLink to="/" className={ ({isActive}) => isActive ? "activeLink" : "nonactiveLink"}>Schedule</NavLink>
            </Button>
            <Button className={styles.link}>
                <NavLink to="/standings" className={ ({isActive}) => isActive ? "activeLink" : "nonactiveLink"}>Standings</NavLink>
            </Button>
            <Button className={styles.link}>
                <NavLink to="/results" className={ ({isActive}) => isActive ? "activeLink" : "nonactiveLink"}>Results</NavLink>
            </Button>
        </nav>
    )
}

export default Navbar
